item.dc:creator: @Rog3r Rog3r
item.description:
@Rog3r wrote:

You can’t bump topics when posting.
You can also not give rep.
You can also not give your IP and port as that is advertising.
You can not double post.

Perhaps the IP is in use, perhaps you didn’t port forward, or perhaps your firewall is blocking connection.
